<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 장바구니 쿠폰</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="layerPop full-size open" >
        <div class="cont">
            <h1 class="layer-title">쿠폰받기</h1>

            <section>
                <div class="dcCouponWrap">
                    <div class="form-flex">
                        <div class="form-flex-cell">
                            <input type="text" placeholder="쿠폰 코드를 입력해 주세요">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-flex-btn">
                            <button class="btn-basicM">등록</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- tip-wrap -->
                    <div class="tip-wrap">
                        <div class="tip">이미 등록한 쿠폰이거나 유효기간이 만료된 쿠폰은 적용이 불가합니다.</div>
                        <div class="tip">본 주문에서만 사용 가능한 쿠폰만 적용할 수 있습니다.</div>
                        <div class="tip">사용하지 않은 쿠폰은 유효기간이 남아있는 경우에 한하여 쿠폰 코드 재적용 후 사용이 가능합니다.</div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- //tip-wrap -->

                    <!-- coupon-wrap -->
                    <div class="coupon-wrap">

                        <ul class="coupon-list">
                            <li>
                                <div class="discount-coupon">
                                    <div class="discount-coupon-inner">
                                        <div class="flex-box">
                                            <div class="dc-rate">
                                                <span class="num">10</span>
                                                <span class="unit">%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="info">
                                                <div class="tit">FW 특별 할인쿠폰 10%</div>
                                                <div class="date">2020.12.01 ~ 2020.12.31</div>
                                                <div class="desc">
                                                    50,000원 이상 구매 시<br>
                                                    최대 100,000원<br>
                                                    (일부 상품 제외)
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="download">
                                                <button type="button">
                                                    <span class="for-a11y">쿠폰받기</span>
                                                </button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div class="discount-coupon">
                                    <div class="discount-coupon-inner">
                                        <div class="flex-box">
                                            <div class="dc-rate">
                                                <span class="num">10</span>
                                                <span class="unit">만원</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="info">
                                                <div class="tit">할인쿠폰 100,000원</div>
                                                <div class="date">2020.12.01 ~ 2020.12.31</div>
                                                <div class="desc">
                                                    50,000원 이상 구매 시<br>
                                                    최대 100,000원<br>
                                                    (일부 상품 제외)
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="download">
                                                <button type="button">
                                                    <span class="for-a11y">쿠폰받기</span>
                                                </button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div class="discount-coupon">
                                    <div class="discount-coupon-inner">
                                        <div class="flex-box">
                                            <div class="dc-rate">
                                                <span class="num">20</span>
                                                <span class="unit">%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="info">
                                                <div class="tit">FW 특별 할인쿠폰 10%</div>
                                                <div class="date">2020.12.01 ~ 2020.12.31</div>
                                                <div class="desc">
                                                    50,000원 이상 구매 시<br>
                                                    최대 100,000원<br>
                                                    (일부 상품 제외)
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="download">
                                                <button type="button">
                                                    <span class="for-a11y">쿠폰받기</span>
                                                </button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <button class="btn-close">팝업닫기</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>